339
00:26:35,894 --> 00:26:41,594
いたずらみたいな奇跡のような刹那
A fleeting moment like a mischievous miracle

340
00:26:41,694 --> 00:26:44,294
あっという間に流れる時が
Time that flows by in the blink of an eye,

341
00:26:44,294 --> 00:26:48,094
ありのままで在り続ける怖さが
and the fear of continuing to stay as we are

342
00:26:48,094 --> 00:26:52,894
失った時間は取り戻せないけれど
We can't take back the lost time, but...

343
00:26:53,094 --> 00:26:55,094
過去を
If you do nothing

344
00:26:55,094 --> 00:26:57,894
振り返ってばかりじゃ
but look back at the past,

345
00:26:57,894 --> 00:26:59,894
泣いたっていいんだ
it's okay to cry

346
00:26:59,894 --> 00:27:02,894
悔しさと痛みだけが
Because only the frustration and pain

347
00:27:02,894 --> 00:27:06,594
君を肯定するから
will validate who you are

348
00:27:06,894 --> 00:27:09,594
大人になったら忘れてしまうの
Will we forget it when we grow up?

349
00:27:09,694 --> 00:27:12,694
君との約束をした場所は
The place where I made a promise with you......

350
00:27:12,694 --> 00:27:14,694
もうない
is no longer there

351
00:27:14,694 --> 00:27:16,894
覚えていたいよ
I want to remember it

352
00:27:16,894 --> 00:27:19,494
思い出も愛しく思えてしまうほど
To the point that even memories feel precious

353
00:27:19,494 --> 00:27:22,094
重ねてしまうよ
I'll keep piling them on

354
00:27:22,094 --> 00:27:25,094
不格好なまんまでいいから
Because it's fine to be clumsy

355
00:27:25,094 --> 00:27:30,094
その声はどこまでも鳴り響いて
Let that voice resound forever and ever

356
00:27:30,594 --> 00:27:33,894
確かな理由を抱いてここまで来たんだ
Holding a certain reason, I've come this far

357
00:27:33,894 --> 00:27:36,594
まだ終わらない旅路なんだ
This is a journey that hasn't ended yet

358
00:27:36,594 --> 00:27:41,594
いつしか想いは形になる
Someday, our feelings will take shape

359
00:27:41,694 --> 00:27:45,594
この真っ白に染まる朝
This morning dyed in pure white

360
00:27:45,594 --> 00:27:47,894
忘れられないまま
Remaining unable to forget,

361
00:27:47,894 --> 00:27:51,594
だから
and so...

362
00:27:55,294 --> 00:27:57,894
諦めてしまうほど
So much that you might give up,

363
00:27:57,894 --> 00:28:01,094
この先たくさんの
there are many...

364
00:28:01,294 --> 00:28:05,894
もうない 迷いはしないよ
No more, I won't hesitate anymore

365
00:28:05,894 --> 00:28:10,094
かけがえのないもの 溢れてしまうよ
The things that are irreplaceable are overflowing

366
00:28:10,094 --> 00:28:13,294
答えは君のその手の中に
The answer is inside your hands

367
00:28:13,294 --> 00:28:15,294
離さないで
Don't let go of it

368
00:28:15,294 --> 00:28:18,594
物語は一歩前へ
The story takes a step forward

369
00:28:20,594 --> 00:28:23,294
諦めてしまうほど
So much that you might give up,

370
00:28:23,294 --> 00:28:25,094
この先たくさんの
there are many

371
00:28:25,094 --> 00:28:27,594
後悔が君を待ってるけど
regrets waiting for you ahead, but...

372
00:28:27,594 --> 00:28:29,894
もうない
No more,

373
00:28:29,894 --> 00:28:32,594
迷いはしないよ
I won't hesitate anymore

374
00:28:32,594 --> 00:28:35,494
この傷も愛しく思えてしまうほど
To the point that even these wounds feel precious

375
00:28:35,494 --> 00:28:37,094
重ねてしまうよ
I'll keep piling them on

376
00:28:37,094 --> 00:28:39,294
不格好なまんまでいいから
Because it's fine to be clumsy

377
00:28:39,294 --> 00:28:41,894
走れ その歩幅で
Run, at your own pace

378
00:28:41,894 --> 00:28:44,294
走れ 声轟かせてくれ
Run, let your voice roar

379
00:28:44,294 --> 00:28:47,094
期待と不安を同じくらい抱きしめて
Embracing both expectations and anxiety in equal measure

380
00:28:47,094 --> 00:28:54,094
君と今を紡ぐ未来照らして
Illuminate the future that weaves "now" with you

381
00:29:28,594 --> 00:29:34,094
六兆年と一夜物語
A Tale of Six Trillion Years and a Night

382
00:29:50,094 --> 00:29:53,094
名もない時代の集落の
In a village of a nameless era,

383
00:29:53,094 --> 00:29:56,094
名もない幼い少年の
lived a nameless young boy,

384
00:29:56,094 --> 00:29:59,994
誰も知らないおとぎばなし
in a fairy tale that no one knows

385
00:30:00,569 --> 00:30:03,469
産まれついた時から
Since the moment I was born,

386
00:30:03,469 --> 00:30:06,469
忌み子 鬼の子として
treated as an unwanted demon child,

387
00:30:06,469 --> 00:30:10,869
その身に余る 罰を受けた
I received a punishment too great for my body to bear.

388
00:30:11,069 --> 00:30:15,569
悲しいことは 何も無いけど
There is nothing to be sad about, but...

389
00:30:15,869 --> 00:30:21,869
夕焼け小焼け 手を引かれてさ
as the sunset glows, my hand is taken and I am led away.

390
00:30:21,969 --> 00:30:24,469
知らない 知らない 僕は何も知らない
I don't know, I don't know, I don't know anything!

391
00:30:24,469 --> 00:30:26,969
叱られた後のやさしさも
Not even the kindness after being scolded,

392
00:30:26,969 --> 00:30:29,469
雨上がりの手の温もりも
nor the warmth of a hand after the rain.

393
00:30:29,469 --> 00:30:32,069
でも本当は 本当は 本当は 本当に
But actually, actually, actually, I am really...

394
00:30:32,069 --> 00:30:33,069
寒いんだ
...so cold.

395
00:30:33,069 --> 00:30:35,569
死なない 死なない 僕はなんで死なない？
I won't die, I won't die, why won't I die?

396
00:30:35,569 --> 00:30:37,469
夢のひとつも 見れないくせに
Even though I can't even have a single dream.

397
00:30:37,469 --> 00:30:39,969
誰も知らない おとぎばなしは
This fairy tale that no one knows

398
00:30:39,969 --> 00:30:43,069
夕焼けの中に吸い込まれて消えてった
was swallowed up by the sunset and disappeared.

399
00:30:52,369 --> 00:30:55,369
吐き出す様な暴力と
With violence spat out like bile,

400
00:30:55,369 --> 00:30:58,369
蔑んだ目の毎日に
and days filled with eyes of contempt,

401
00:30:58,369 --> 00:31:02,869
君はいつしか そこに立ってた
before I knew it, you were standing there.

402
00:31:03,069 --> 00:31:05,769
話しかけちゃだめなのに
Even though I wasn't supposed to speak to you,

403
00:31:05,769 --> 00:31:08,569
「君の名前が知りたいな」
"I want to know your name."

404
00:31:08,769 --> 00:31:13,069
ごめんね 名前も 舌も無いんだ
I'm sorry, I have no name, nor a tongue.

405
00:31:13,069 --> 00:31:18,069
僕の居場所は 何処にも無いのに
Even though there is no place for me anywhere,

406
00:31:18,069 --> 00:31:23,969
「一緒に帰ろう」 手を引かれてさ
"Let's go home together," you said, taking my hand.

407
00:31:23,969 --> 00:31:26,469
知らない 知らない 僕は何も知らない
I don't know, I don't know, I don't know anything!

408
00:31:26,469 --> 00:31:28,969
君はもう子供じゃないことも
Not even that you are no longer a child,

409
00:31:28,969 --> 00:31:31,469
慣れない他人の 手の温もりは
nor that the unfamiliar warmth of someone else's hand

410
00:31:31,469 --> 00:31:34,069
ただ本当に 本当に 本当に 本当のことなんだ
is actually, actually, actually, truly real.

411
00:31:34,069 --> 00:31:36,469
やめない やめない 君はなんでやめない？
You won't stop, you won't stop, why won't you stop?

412
00:31:36,469 --> 00:31:38,969
見つかれば殺されちゃうくせに
Even though you'll be killed if they find you.

413
00:31:38,969 --> 00:31:41,469
雨上がりに 忌み子がふたり
Two unwanted children after the rain,

414
00:31:41,469 --> 00:31:45,069
夕焼けの中に吸い込まれて消えてった
were swallowed up by the sunset and disappeared.

415
00:31:54,369 --> 00:31:57,069
日が暮れて 夜が明けて
The sun set, the night broke,

416
00:31:57,069 --> 00:32:00,069
遊び疲れて つかまって
we grew tired of playing and were caught.

417
00:32:00,069 --> 00:32:04,969
こんな世界 僕と君以外 みんな居なくなればいいのにな
In a world like this, I wish everyone but you and me would disappear...

418
00:32:04,969 --> 00:32:08,569
みんな居なくなればいいのにな
I wish everyone else would just disappear.

419
00:32:08,569 --> 00:32:11,069
知らない 知らない 声が聞こえてさ
I don't know, I don't know, but a voice can be heard!

420
00:32:11,069 --> 00:32:13,969
僕と君以外の 全人類
Every single human being besides you and me,

421
00:32:13,969 --> 00:32:19,069
抗う間もなく 手を引かれてさ
without even time to resist, was led away by the hand,

422
00:32:19,069 --> 00:32:22,069
夕焼けの中に吸い込まれて消えてった
and swallowed up by the sunset, disappearing.

423
00:32:22,069 --> 00:32:24,469
知らない 知らない 僕は何も知らない
I don't know, I don't know, I don't know anything!

424
00:32:24,469 --> 00:32:26,969
これからのことも 君の名も
Not what lies ahead, nor your name.

425
00:32:26,969 --> 00:32:29,469
今は 今は これでいいんだと
But for now, for now, "this is fine,"

426
00:32:29,469 --> 00:32:32,069
ただ本当に 本当に 本当に 本当に思うんだ
is what I truly, truly, truly, truly believe.

427
00:32:32,069 --> 00:32:34,469
知らない 知らない あの耳鳴りは
I don't know, I don't know, but that ringing in my ears...

428
00:32:34,469 --> 00:32:37,069
夕焼けの中に吸い込まれて消えてった
was swallowed up by the sunset and disappeared.

429
00:33:19,569 --> 00:33:21,269
風を置いて
Leaving the wind behind,

430
00:33:21,269 --> 00:33:24,269
雨を抜けて
breaking through the rain,

431
00:33:24,269 --> 00:33:28,069
咲き誇れ
bloom in full glory!

432
00:33:28,569 --> 00:33:38,069
Star-mine
[Title: Star-mine]

433
00:33:38,269 --> 00:33:40,869
あぁ、夜風に揺られている
Ah, swayed by the night breeze,

434
00:33:40,869 --> 00:33:43,369
折れないように 怯えている
terrified of breaking.

435
00:33:43,369 --> 00:33:45,869
ずっと雨に濡らされている
Soaked continuously by the rain,

436
00:33:45,869 --> 00:33:49,069
またどうしたって 凍えてしまったんだ
once again, I've ended up freezing.

437
00:33:49,069 --> 00:33:51,569
誰か この声に 応答して
Someone, please answer this voice...

438
00:33:51,569 --> 00:33:54,069
痛がるばっかで
As it only hurts,

439
00:33:54,069 --> 00:33:58,069
咲けないままの ハートを
...this heart that is unable to bloom.

440
00:33:58,069 --> 00:34:02,569
あぁ、今 見逃せないくらい 綺麗に
Ah, right now, so beautifully that you can't look away,

441
00:34:02,569 --> 00:34:07,069
咲かせたいんだ
I want to make it bloom!

442
00:34:07,069 --> 00:34:09,569
光っていた未来が
The future that was shining,

443
00:34:09,569 --> 00:34:11,869
ずっと待っていた世界が
and the world that had been waiting all along,

444
00:34:11,869 --> 00:34:16,269
きらめく音の中にあるなら
if they are within this sparkling sound...

445
00:34:16,269 --> 00:34:18,569
最低で 最悪な涙も
Then even the lowest, worst tears,

446
00:34:18,569 --> 00:34:21,569
痛がりで 嫌いな声も
and the painful, hated voice,

447
00:34:21,569 --> 00:34:26,569
連れていきたいんだ 全部
I want to take them all along!

448
00:34:26,569 --> 00:34:29,069
不完全な 毎日が
These incomplete everyday lives,

449
00:34:29,069 --> 00:34:31,569
一瞬のカケラたちが
and the fragments of moments,

450
00:34:31,569 --> 00:34:36,069
重なって こんな歌を奏でたら
if they overlap and play a song like this...

451
00:34:36,069 --> 00:34:37,069
それは
...then that,

452
00:34:37,069 --> 00:34:41,269
言葉だけじゃ 届かない距離を
surely leaps over the distance that words alone cannot reach,

453
00:34:41,269 --> 00:34:45,869
きっと飛び越えて 結ぶ
connecting us together.

454
00:34:45,869 --> 00:34:50,069
きっと輪を描いていく
Surely, it will draw a circle.

455
00:35:00,117 --> 00:35:01,917
一・二・三・四・五・六・ステップ踏んで
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, take a step,

456
00:35:01,917 --> 00:35:04,317
ほら 波に乗って 気取って 浮いて
look, ride the wave, show off, and float.

457
00:35:04,317 --> 00:35:06,117
手を回せ 回せ グルーヴを回せ
Spin your hands, spin them, spin the groove,

458
00:35:06,117 --> 00:35:08,617
フワッとステップ踏んで 今夜は止まんない
take a light step, tonight we won't stop.

459
00:35:08,617 --> 00:35:11,317
迷ったら踊れ 事態は切実さ
If you're hesitant, dance! The situation is urgent,

460
00:35:11,317 --> 00:35:13,917
お構いなしの稲妻鳴らして
