461
00:35:13,917 --> 00:35:18,117
声を枯らせ 泥だらけになってもいい 生きていたい
Let your voice go hoarse, it's okay to get muddy, I want to live!

462
00:35:18,117 --> 00:35:22,617
今夜 あの空で合流して
Tonight, let's meet up in that sky,

463
00:35:22,617 --> 00:35:25,117
朝が満たすまで
until the morning fills us.

464
00:35:25,117 --> 00:35:28,117
それぞれの星を探そう
Let's look for our respective stars.

465
00:35:28,117 --> 00:35:30,317
ねえ 今
Hey, right now,

466
00:35:30,317 --> 00:35:33,817
同じこと思っていたんだって
you were thinking the same thing, right?

467
00:35:33,817 --> 00:35:37,117
ほら 話さなくても分かり合えた
Look, we understood each other without even speaking.

468
00:35:37,117 --> 00:35:41,617
あぁ こんな嬉しさを
Ah, this kind of happiness...

469
00:35:41,617 --> 00:35:46,117
ずっと歌ってみたかった
I've always wanted to sing about it.

470
00:35:47,617 --> 00:35:51,117
光っていた未来が ずっと待っていた世界が
Because the shining future and the world we've been waiting for

471
00:35:51,117 --> 00:35:55,917
きらめいて目の前にあるから
are glittering right in front of us.

472
00:35:55,917 --> 00:36:00,117
瞬きの刹那まで このストーリーの最後まで
Until the blink of an eye, until the end of this story,

473
00:36:00,117 --> 00:36:06,617
輝く花でいたいんだ
I want to remain a shining flower.

474
00:36:06,617 --> 00:36:10,117
不完全な私たちが 一瞬の欠片たちが
If our imperfect selves, these fragments of a moment,

475
00:36:10,117 --> 00:36:15,917
重なって今度こそ奏でたら
overlap and play together this time,

476
00:36:15,917 --> 00:36:21,117
それは夢見るだけじゃ叶わない想いをずっと新しくしてく
it will keep renewing the feelings that won't come true just by dreaming.

477
00:36:25,617 --> 00:36:28,617
ずっと追いかけていこう
Let's keep chasing them forever.

478
00:36:28,617 --> 00:36:31,317
風を抱いて
Embracing the wind,

479
00:36:31,317 --> 00:36:33,917
雨を抜けて
passing through the rain,

480
00:36:33,917 --> 00:36:36,617
咲き誇れ
bloom in full glory

481
00:36:36,617 --> 00:36:46,117
満天の空へ
towards the star-filled sky!

482
00:37:27,317 --> 00:37:30,117
世界中のすべての人間に好かれるなんて気持ち悪いよ
It's creepy to be liked by everyone in this world.

483
00:37:30,117 --> 00:37:31,817
だけど一つになれない教室で
But in a classroom where we can't become one,

484
00:37:31,817 --> 00:37:34,117
君と二人 手を繋いでいたいの
I want to hold hands with you, just the two of us.

485
00:37:34,117 --> 00:37:35,517
数の暴力に白旗をあげて
I'll raise the white flag to the tyranny of numbers,

486
00:37:35,517 --> 00:37:37,117
悪感情を殺してハイチーズ
suppress my ill feelings and say cheese.

487
00:37:37,117 --> 00:37:38,917
ポストトゥルースの甘いディープキス
A sweet, post-truth deep kiss...

488
00:37:38,917 --> 00:37:40,617
エロく歪んでるラブアンドピース
A warped, erotic love and peace.

489
00:37:40,617 --> 00:37:42,317
自己中の光線銃 乱射する
Firing a self-centered ray gun wildly,

490
00:37:42,317 --> 00:37:43,917
強者のナンセンス
the nonsense of the strong.

491
00:37:43,917 --> 00:37:45,417
オートクチュールで作る
Creating with haute couture

492
00:37:45,417 --> 00:37:47,117
殺しのライセンス
a license to kill.

493
00:37:47,117 --> 00:37:48,617
分断を生んじゃった椅子取りゲーム
A game of musical chairs that created division,

494
00:37:48,617 --> 00:37:50,217
無痛分娩で授かるベイブ
a baby born through painless labor.

495
00:37:50,217 --> 00:37:52,117
壮大な内輪ノリを歴史と呼ぶ
We're calling a grandiose in-joke "history."

496
00:37:52,117 --> 00:37:53,717
生きたいが死ねと言われ
I want to live but I'm told to die.

497
00:37:53,717 --> 00:37:55,217
死にたいが生きろと言われ
I want to die but I'm told to live.

498
00:37:55,217 --> 00:37:56,917
生きたいが死ねと言われ
I want to live but I'm told to die.

499
00:37:56,917 --> 00:37:58,617
死にたいが生きろと言われ
I want to die but I'm told to live.

500
00:37:58,617 --> 00:38:00,117
幸せ自慢はダメ？
Is it wrong to boast of my happiness?

501
00:38:00,117 --> 00:38:01,917
不幸嘆いてもダメ？
Is it wrong to grieve over my unhappiness?

502
00:38:01,917 --> 00:38:03,617
図々しい言葉を避け
Avoiding impudent words,

503
00:38:03,617 --> 00:38:05,617
明るい未来のため
for our glorious future.

504
00:38:05,617 --> 00:38:06,617
さんはい
One, two...

505
00:38:06,617 --> 00:38:09,317
「この世には息もできない人が沢山いるんですよ」
"There are many people in this world who can't even breathe."

506
00:38:09,317 --> 00:38:10,117
さんはい
One, two...

507
00:38:10,117 --> 00:38:12,617
「この世には息もできない人が沢山いるんですよ」
"There are many people in this world who can't even breathe."

508
00:38:12,617 --> 00:38:14,117
あちらが立てば こちらが立たず
If I'm true to one side, I'm false to the other.

509
00:38:14,117 --> 00:38:15,917
譲り 奪い 守り 行き違い
We give, we take, we protect, we misunderstand.

510
00:38:15,917 --> 00:38:17,617
地雷原で立ち止まり
Stopping in the minefield...

511
00:38:17,617 --> 00:38:19,117
大人しく犬になるんだワン
I'll obediently become a dog, woof.

512
