Choose one of them!

667
00:50:30,115 --> 00:50:32,115
両方はちょっとあれだから...
Voting for both is a bit tricky, so...

668
00:50:32,115 --> 00:50:35,115
どっちか、どっちかにお願いします！
Please pick one or the other!

669
00:50:35,115 --> 00:50:38,315
そういえば、今なんだかんだこうやって歩かせてもらっていますが...
By the way, as I walk along like this...

670
00:50:38,315 --> 00:50:41,115
実はね、何気にね...
Actually, you know...

671
00:50:41,115 --> 00:50:44,315
ファーストミッション衣装がね...
Showing off this First Mission Outfit...

672
00:50:44,315 --> 00:50:47,115
見せるのが、ゆっくり見せるのが、初めてだったりするんだけど...
and showing it slowly is actually a first...

673
00:50:47,115 --> 00:50:49,115
そうだ、ここでさ、宣伝しとこう。
Oh right, let me do some promo here.

674
00:50:49,115 --> 00:50:52,115
尺稼ぎじゃないよ！あれ、宣伝ね。
This isn't just to fill time! It's promo, okay?

675
00:50:52,115 --> 00:50:55,315
このあとメインでアフターライブがあるんですけど...
We have an after-live on the main stage next...

676
00:50:55,315 --> 00:50:57,915
その時、その時に、もっとこのカッコいいところを...
and at that time, I'll show you many more...

677
00:50:57,915 --> 00:51:00,115
いっぱい見せますので！
of these cool features!

678
00:51:00,115 --> 00:51:03,115
なんでぜひ良かったらメインのアフターライブにも...
So please, if you'd like, come to the main...

679
00:51:03,115 --> 00:51:06,115
お越しください！っていう宣伝も入れつつ...
after-live! Throwing in that quick promo...

680
00:51:06,115 --> 00:51:08,615
みんな入れた？
Did everyone vote?

681
00:51:08,615 --> 00:51:10,615
みんな入れた？
Did you all vote?

682
00:51:10,615 --> 00:51:13,615
すごっ、何これ？花道、長くない？
Wow, what is this? Isn't the runway long?

683
00:51:13,615 --> 00:51:15,615
な、長くない？
I-Isn't it really long?

684
00:51:18,115 --> 00:51:21,115
これ、これ現地ライブでもやりたいな。
I'd love to do this at an in-person live show.

685
00:51:21,115 --> 00:51:24,615
はい、もう大分カッコいい風真いろはをいっぱい見せているわけなんですが。
Yes, I've already been showing you a very cool side of myself.

686
00:51:24,615 --> 00:51:26,615
いや、でもどっちかな？これ。
But I wonder which one it'll be?

687
00:51:26,615 --> 00:51:29,115
「ANIMA」はね、みんな。設定の通りの「ANIMA」。
"ANIMA" is, you know, just like the setting.

688
00:51:29,115 --> 00:51:31,115
カッコいい！カッコいい！で。
It's so cool!

689
00:51:31,115 --> 00:51:34,115
「ただ声一つ」はしっとり。しっとり、なんで。
While "Tada Koe Hitotsu" is mellow and emotional.

690
00:51:34,115 --> 00:51:37,115
これ好みが分かれると思います。はい、いや、きっとね...
So, preferences might be divided. But surely...

691
00:51:37,115 --> 00:51:41,115
どっちやってもみんなカッコいいって言ってくれるよね？
Whichever it is, you'll still say I'm cool, right?

692
00:51:41,115 --> 00:51:42,615
言ってくれるよね？
You will, right?

693
00:51:42,615 --> 00:51:45,615
え、言って、言ってくれる？あ、言ってくれる！
Wait, will you? Oh, you will!

694
00:51:45,615 --> 00:51:48,115
カメラは言ってくれるということで。
The camera operator nodded yes, so...

695
00:51:48,115 --> 00:51:50,115
はい、というわけで、みんな、もう大丈夫かな？
Alright, so is everyone ready?

696
00:51:50,115 --> 00:51:51,615
オッケー？
Are we good?

697
00:51:51,615 --> 00:51:53,115
じゃあ、そろそろ終わっちゃいますからね。
Then, it's about time to close it.

698
00:51:53,115 --> 00:51:56,115
はい、早く早く、早く投票してね！
Hurry up and cast your votes quickly!

699
00:51:59,615 --> 00:52:01,115
はい、はい、え？
Yes, yes, eh?

700
00:52:01,115 --> 00:52:04,115
終わった？終わったよね？スタッフさん、終わった？
Is it over? It's over, right? Staff, is it done?

701
00:52:04,115 --> 00:52:06,115
終わった？
Is it over?

702
00:52:06,115 --> 00:52:08,615
早かった？歩くの。終わった？
Was my walking too fast? Is it done?

703
00:52:08,615 --> 00:52:11,115
終わった、終わった、終わったかな？
I wonder if it's finished?

704
00:52:11,115 --> 00:52:13,115
あ、なんか終わったらしい。
Ah, looks like it's over.

705
00:52:13,115 --> 00:52:16,615
今、賭けをしているスタッフと睨めっこしてます。
Right now, I'm staring down the staff who placed a bet.

706
00:52:16,615 --> 00:52:19,115
それでは！
Now then!

707
00:52:19,115 --> 00:52:21,615
結果発表タイム！
Time to announce the results!

708
00:52:27,615 --> 00:52:29,115
じゃん！
Ta-da!

709
00:52:30,115 --> 00:52:35,115
アンケートの結果、「ANIMA」になったみたいです！
According to the poll, it looks like it's "ANIMA"!

710
00:52:38,115 --> 00:52:41,315
これ、あの賭けに勝った人の動きです。
This is the victory dance of someone who won the bet.

711
00:52:41,315 --> 00:52:44,315
うぇーい！差し入れ期待してます！よっしゃー！
Yay! I'll be expecting treats! All right!

712
00:52:45,115 --> 00:52:48,615
というわけで、あの賭けにも勝ち、皆さんにも選んでいただき、とてもありがたい限りですね。
So, winning the bet and being chosen by everyone, I'm super grateful.

713
00:52:48,615 --> 00:52:54,115
「ただ声一つ」の方もこのあとメンバーシップ限定で歌いますので、そちらもお楽しみに！
I'll also sing "Tada Koe Hitotsu" on membership after, so look forward to that!

714
00:52:55,115 --> 00:52:58,615
と、いうわけで、早速歌っていきましょうか。
And with that, let's start singing right away.

715
00:52:59,115 --> 00:53:04,115
それでは聞いてください。「ANIMA」。
Now, please listen to "ANIMA".

716
00:53:07,615 --> 00:53:10,615
魂の色は
What color is...

717
00:53:10,615 --> 00:53:13,615
何色ですか
...the color of your soul?

718
00:53:25,115 --> 00:53:27,615
「もういっそ 折れたままで」
"I'd rather it stay broken."

719
00:53:27,615 --> 00:53:31,115
捨てるほど 逃げ出すほど
So much that I'd throw it away, run away from it...

720
00:53:31,115 --> 00:53:34,115
強くないよ ほら
I'm not that strong, you see...

721
00:53:34,115 --> 00:53:37,115
もう一度 鼓動 高鳴る
Once again, my heartbeat quickens.

722
00:53:37,115 --> 00:53:40,615
何が正しいかなんて
As to what is right,

723
00:53:40,615 --> 00:53:44,615
わからないけど
I still do not know, but...

724
00:53:45,115 --> 00:53:48,615
形のないものばかりが
Only the things without shape...

725
00:53:48,615 --> 00:53:52,615
大切になって行く
...become more and more precious.

726
00:53:55,415 --> 00:53:59,115
飾らない言葉だけが
Only those unadorned words

727
00:53:59,115 --> 00:54:03,115
強く結ばれてる
are tightly bound together.

728
00:54:05,315 --> 00:54:09,615
また躓いて 転がって それでも砕けない
Tripping and falling again, yet still unbreakable.

729
00:54:09,615 --> 00:54:14,615
魂の色は 何色ですか
What color is the color of your soul?

730
00:54:15,115 --> 00:54:19,615
ただ傷ついて 強がって それでも見つけたいよ
Just getting hurt, acting tough, yet still wanting to find...

731
00:54:19,615 --> 00:54:24,615
魂のカタチ 確かめてるよ
...and confirm the shape of my soul.

732
00:54:36,115 --> 00:54:39,115
深い地の底で一人
Alone deep under the earth,

733
00:54:39,115 --> 00:54:42,615
扉と鍵を探す
searching for the door and the key.

734
00:54:42,615 --> 00:54:45,315
おとぎ話は ほら
Fairy tales, you see,

735
00:54:45,315 --> 00:54:49,115
泡の様に全部消えて
disappear completely like bubbles,

736
00:54:49,115 --> 00:54:52,615
葛藤 残像だけ
leaving only struggles and afterimages.

737
00:54:52,615 --> 00:54:55,615
次の頁へ
Onto the next page...

738
00:54:55,615 --> 00:55:00,115
伸びてく枝葉が分かれて それぞれの道を行く
Sprouting branches split, each going its own way.

739
00:55:00,163 --> 00:55:03,963
それぞれの道を行く
...and go our separate ways.

740
00:55:05,863 --> 00:55:09,763
寂しい思い出だけが
Only the lonely memories...

741
00:55:10,663 --> 00:55:14,763
強く根を張ってる
...are taking deep root.

742
00:55:18,963 --> 00:55:23,063
まだ貫いて失って それでも挫けない
I still stand firm and lose, but even so, I won't lose heart.

743
00:55:23,363 --> 00:55:27,863
心はどこに 器はどこに
Where is the heart? Where is the vessel?

744
00:55:28,163 --> 00:55:32,563
ただ残されて抜け落ちて それでも伝えたいよ
I'm just left behind and falling out, but even so, I want to convey...

745
00:55:33,363 --> 00:55:38,363
魂の日々を 魂の意志を
...the days of the soul, the will of the soul...

746
00:55:38,963 --> 00:55:43,163
ずっと
...forever.

747
00:55:43,163 --> 00:55:48,963
ずっと
Forever...

748
00:56:11,163 --> 00:56:14,963
魂の色は
What color is the soul?

749
00:56:15,663 --> 00:56:19,563
何色ですか
What color is it?

750
00:56:20,263 --> 00:56:24,563
赤色ですか
Is it red?

751
00:56:25,163 --> 00:56:29,563
青色ですか
Is it blue?

752
00:56:30,463 --> 00:56:34,663
魂の色は
What color is the soul?

753
00:56:34,763 --> 00:56:39,563
何色ですか
What color is it?

754
00:56:40,563 --> 00:56:44,863
透明な過去に 不透明な明日に
In the transparent past, in the unclear tomorrow...

755
00:56:45,163 --> 00:56:49,663
生きるあなたは何色ですか
...what color are you, living your life?

756
00:56:51,363 --> 00:56:55,863
また躓いて転がって それでも砕けない
I stumble and fall again, but even so, I won't break.

757
00:56:56,363 --> 00:57:00,763
魂の色は 何色ですか
What color is the soul? What color is it?

758
00:57:01,163 --> 00:57:05,763
ただ傷ついて強がって それでも見つけたいよ
I'm just hurt and acting tough, but even so, I want to find it...

759
00:57:06,163 --> 00:57:11,163
魂のカタチ 確かめてるよ
...I am verifying the shape of the soul.

760
00:57:11,363 --> 00:57:16,163
ずっと
Forever...

761
00:57:16,163 --> 00:57:21,163
ずっと
...forever...

762
00:57:21,163 --> 00:57:25,963
ずっと
...forever...

763
00:57:25,963 --> 00:57:32,163
ずっと
...forever.

764
00:57:39,163 --> 00:57:41,363
はい！ということで
All right! And so,

765
00:57:41,363 --> 00:57:44,963
ANIMAを歌わせていただきました！
I performed "ANIMA"!

766
00:57:46,163 --> 00:57:50,163
カロリー高いほうだったな、水、水ください
That was a high-calorie song! Water, please give me some water.

767
00:57:51,763 --> 00:57:53,763
カロリー高いほうだった
That was really high-calorie...

768
00:57:53,963 --> 00:57:55,163
あぶない
That was close.

769
00:58:00,963 --> 00:58:05,363
あ、すいません。あの、ナチュラルにマイクを返すの忘れていました。
Ah, sorry. I totally forgot to return the mic.

770
00:58:06,163 --> 00:58:10,163
やばい、音変になってなかったならいいな、すいません。
Oh dear, I hope the sound didn't go weird. Sorry!

771
00:58:10,663 --> 00:58:17,663
ナチュラルのに。スタッフさんがすっごい手伸ばしてくれたのに、疲れすぎでここ硬直しちゃってた。
I naturally... The staff was stretching their arm out so far, but I was so tired my arm just froze.

772
00:58:18,163 --> 00:58:19,163
はーい
Okay.

773
00:58:19,963 --> 00:58:21,563
水うまい
Water tastes so good.

774
00:58:22,963 --> 00:58:26,663
減らない水のおかげで、生きていけてます。
Thanks to this bottomless water, I'm able to survive.

775
00:58:27,163 --> 00:58:29,163
はい、で、ちょっとこれ返して。
All right, let me return this.

776
00:58:31,163 --> 00:58:32,563
はい！
Okay!

777
00:58:32,563 --> 00:58:35,963
それではですね、ま、ちょっとまだまだ続くんですけど、
So, well, there's still more to come,

778
00:58:36,163 --> 00:58:41,363
ここいらで一旦、重大告知タイムをさせていただきたいと思います！
but at this point, I'd like to have a major announcement time!

779
00:58:42,163 --> 00:58:44,963
じゃ、まずはいつものから行くか！じゃ、まずはこちら！
First, let's start with the usual one! Here it is!

780
00:58:45,163 --> 00:58:50,563
風真いろは、誕生日記念グッズ2026出ます！
Kazama Iroha Birthday Celebration Goods 2026 are coming out!

781
00:58:50,563 --> 00:58:53,763
ドンドコドンドン、ドンドンドン！
Dondokodondon, dondondon!

782
00:58:54,163 --> 00:58:58,163
いや、なんか良さそうなラインナップですね。
Wow, it looks like a really great lineup!

783
00:58:58,163 --> 00:59:03,363
はい、今回もとってもこだわったグッズばかりなんで、皆さん楽しみにしていてほしいです！
Yes, this time too, they're all merchandise we put a lot of care into, so please look forward to them!

784
00:59:03,563 --> 00:59:06,963
では、一つずつ、商品を見ていきましょう。
Now, let's take a look at the items one by one.

785
00:59:07,663 --> 00:59:09,363
まずはこちら！
First is this one!

786
00:59:09,363 --> 00:59:12,763
タペストリーが出ます！
The tapestry is coming!

787
00:59:13,163 --> 00:59:17,163
タペストリー、実は個人グッズで出すの超久しぶりなんですよね。
Actually, it's been a very long time since I last released a tapestry as personal merchandise.

788
00:59:17,163 --> 00:59:22,163
イラストは、もちぷよ先生描き下ろしで、雨上がりの青空の下で
The illustration is drawn by Mochipuyo-sensei. Under the blue sky after the rain,

789
00:59:22,163 --> 00:59:27,163
本当にね、このステージみたいな感じで、ライブをしている風真いろはのイメージで描いていただきました。
she drew it with the image of Kazama Iroha performing a live show, just like on this stage.

790
00:59:27,163 --> 00:59:29,563
ありがとうございます！
Thank you so much!

791
00:59:29,563 --> 00:59:32,163
いや、めっちゃ良いよね。飾ってね！
Wow, it's really nice. Please hang it up!

792
00:59:32,163 --> 00:59:33,363
続いてはこちら！
Next is this one!

793
00:59:33,363 --> 00:59:36,363
フード付きタオル！
The hooded towel!

794
00:59:36,363 --> 00:59:40,163
はい、タペストリーと同じイラストのフード付きタオルです。
Yes, it's a hooded towel with the same illustration as the tapestry.

795
00:59:40,163 --> 00:59:44,363
フード部分はぽこべぇの顔になっており、取り外しが可能となっております。
The hood part has Pokobe's face and is detachable.

796
00:59:44,363 --> 00:59:48,163
いやなんか、こないだね、あの、HoloXのライブあったじゃん？
You know, the other day, there was the HoloX live show, right?

797
00:59:48,163 --> 00:59:52,163
で、なんかダンスの先生に教えてもらったんだけど、
And my dance teacher told me about it,

798
00:59:52,163 --> 00:59:56,363
なんか風真いろは、異様にタオル購入率が良かったらしいな、お前たち。
but apparently, you guys had an unusually high purchase rate for Kazama's towel!

799
00:59:56,363 --> 00:59:59,163
首にいっぱい巻いてくれてえらいぞ！
Good job wrapping them all around your necks!

800
00:59:59,163 --> 01:00:00,163
フード付きタオル！
A hooded towel!

801
01:00:00,138 --> 01:00:03,538
取り外せるんで、これで自忍ぽこべえごっこができるようになります
Since it's removable, you can play-act as Jinin Pokobe with this!

802
01:00:03,538 --> 01:00:05,238
自忍ぽこべえごっこをしたい方
For those of you who want to play as Jinin Pokobe,

803
01:00:05,238 --> 01:00:08,138
まあ、取り外してそのまま飾りたい方もね、どうぞ！
or if you just want to remove it and display it, please go ahead!

804
01:00:08,138 --> 01:00:09,738
はい、そしてお次はこちら！
Alright, and next up is this!

805
01:00:09,738 --> 01:00:13,538
ペットボトルホルダー！
A PET bottle holder!

806
01:00:13,538 --> 01:00:16,938
あの、これは風真いろはさんが欲しいのを作りました！
Um, I made this because it's something I really wanted!

807
01:00:16,938 --> 01:00:20,238
あの、イラストはさめあんこ先生に描いていただきました
The illustration was drawn by Sameanko-sensei.

808
01:00:20,238 --> 01:00:21,938
可愛いでしょ？この真ん中の穴に
Isn't it cute? In this middle hole,

809
01:00:21,938 --> 01:00:24,538
あの、ギュッてペットボトルのところを入れてね
you tightly insert the neck of the PET bottle,

810
01:00:24,538 --> 01:00:26,438
あの、使うやつです、はい
and that's how you use it. Yes!

811
01:00:26,438 --> 01:00:28,538
めちゃくちゃおしゃれです、よかったら使ってください
It's very stylish, so please use it if you'd like.

812
01:00:28,538 --> 01:00:31,638
カバンとかね、付けて持ち運べるんでね
You can attach it to your bag to carry it around!

813
01:00:31,638 --> 01:00:33,338
はい！
Yes!

814
01:00:33,338 --> 01:00:35,038
そしてラストはこちら！
And finally, here's the last one!

815
01:00:35,038 --> 01:00:39,638
はい！実は地味になかった、セーラー服衣装の風真いろはのぬいぐるみ！
Yes! A sailor uniform version of my plushie, which surprisingly didn't exist before!

816
01:00:39,638 --> 01:00:42,638
なんと、ボイス付きです！
And it actually comes with voices!

817
01:00:42,638 --> 01:00:45,438
こちらもさめあんこ先生に原案考えていただきました
Sameanko-sensei also designed the draft for this.

818
01:00:45,438 --> 01:00:48,938
レインポンチョを着た、声が出るぬいぐるみです
It's a voice-playing plushie wearing a rain poncho.

819
01:00:48,938 --> 01:00:52,538
まあ、あの、お腹を握りしめると音が出るらしいぞ
Apparently, it plays sound when you squeeze its tummy!

820
01:00:52,538 --> 01:00:54,538
今のところはな、はい！
At least, for now. Yes!

821
01:00:54,538 --> 01:00:57,238
外出時にカバンなどに付けることもできます。で、ボイスなんですけど
You can also attach it to your bag when you go out. And about the voices...

822
01:00:57,238 --> 01:01:00,738
なんか、天気に関するものを録ったんですよ
I actually recorded things related to the weather!

823
01:01:00,738 --> 01:01:04,738
どんな感じかはまだね、さすがに言えないけど。だけど、あの
I can't tell you exactly what it's like yet, of course. But...

824
01:01:04,738 --> 01:01:07,238
おみくじ感覚で聞いて
you can listen to it like a fortune-telling slip,

825
01:01:07,238 --> 01:01:10,438
あの、その天気にならなかったからと言って、風真いろはを責めないでください
so please don't blame me if the weather doesn't turn out that way!

826
01:01:10,438 --> 01:01:13,338
自己責任で、にぎにぎしてください
Please squeeze it at your own risk!

827
01:01:13,338 --> 01:01:15,638
買ってからのお楽しみです！
Look forward to it after you buy it!

828
01:01:15,638 --> 01:01:17,738
いっぱいありましたが、フルセットを見ていきましょう！
We had a lot of items, but let's check out the full set!

829
01:01:17,738 --> 01:01:19,538
こちら！
Here it is!

830
01:01:19,538 --> 01:01:23,338
今回のグッズはですね、生誕のイメージに合わせてフェス風をテーマに作ってみました
This time, we created the merchandise with a festival theme to match my birthday image.

831
01:01:23,338 --> 01:01:25,938
実用性たっぷりだし、これからの季節にぴったりなんで
It's very practical and perfect for the upcoming season,

832
01:01:25,938 --> 01:01:29,938
よかったら、よろしくお願いします！
so I'd appreciate it if you checked it out!

833
01:01:29,938 --> 01:01:33,338
そしてフルセット購入特典は、こちら！
And the purchase bonus for the full set is this!

834
01:01:33,338 --> 01:01:37,538
数量限定版あります。風真いろはの
There is a limited-quantity version. It includes

835
01:01:37,538 --> 01:01:42,638
直筆サインと箔押し複製メッセージ入りチケット風カード、ちょっとおしゃれな感じですね
a ticket-style card with my handwritten signature and a foil-stamped message. It has a classy feel to it!

836
01:01:42,638 --> 01:01:47,938
そして通常版には、箔押し複製サインとメッセージ入りチケット風カードがついてきます保存版
And the standard version comes with a ticket-style card featuring a foil-stamped signature and message.

837
01:01:47,938 --> 01:01:52,338
えー、さらにどちらにも、えー、ボイスがついてきますね、はい
Furthermore, both versions come with a voice recording. Yes!

838
01:01:52,338 --> 01:01:56,638
「きみと雨宿り」というなんかタイトルのボイスがついてくるんですけど、まあ、ぶっちゃけあの
It's a voice track titled "Sheltering from the Rain with You." Frankly, though...

839
01:01:56,638 --> 01:01:59,338
気になったら聴いてください
please listen to it if you're curious!

840
01:01:59,338 --> 01:02:04,738
ボイスは無理に聴かせたいからね
I really want you to hear this voice track!

841
01:02:04,738 --> 01:02:09,638
はい、ということで、シチュエーションボイスですね。雨宿り系だった気が
Yes, so it's a situation voice. I think it was a sheltering-from-the-rain situation...

842
01:02:09,638 --> 01:02:12,838
なんか照れながら録った気がします！
I feel like I recorded it while feeling embarrassed!

843
01:02:12,838 --> 01:02:15,638
そしてグッズは21時カートオープンです！
And the merchandise cart opens at 21:00!

844
01:02:15,638 --> 01:02:19,538
すみません、あの、生配信につきちょっと時間が押しそうなんですけど
I'm sorry, since this is a live broadcast, we're running a bit behind schedule...

845
01:02:19,538 --> 01:02:22,138
あの、ゆっくり買ってねとは言えず
I can't tell you to take your time buying,

846
01:02:22,138 --> 01:02:26,638
頑張ってください！どうしようもない、ごめん！
so do your best! There's nothing I can do, sorry!

847
01:02:26,638 --> 01:02:32,538
そしてあの、21時からホロメンの多分配信控えてると思うんですけど、あの、何も気にしなくていいんでスタートしてくださいね、はい！
And also, around 21:00, other Hololive members' streams are probably scheduled, but please don't worry about me and just start them, okay? Yes!

848
01:02:32,538 --> 01:02:34,538
はい！そして
Yes! And...

849
01:02:34,538 --> 01:02:36,638
まだまだあります！
there's still more!

850
01:02:36,638 --> 01:02:38,938
まだまだ！それがこちら！
Still more! Here it is!

851
01:02:38,938 --> 01:02:40,938
はい、新曲！
Yes, a new song!

852
01:02:40,938 --> 01:02:43,138
イェーイ！
Yay!

853
01:02:43,138 --> 01:02:47,438
風真いろはさんの新曲が出ます。タイトルは「風向きエントロピー」
I'm releasing a new song! The title is "Kazamuki Entropy."

854
01:02:47,438 --> 01:02:53,138
作詞作曲は「いろはステップ」でもおなじみ、40mPさんにしていただきました！
The lyrics and music were written by 40mP-san, who is also known for "Iroha Step"!

855
01:02:53,138 --> 01:02:54,738
はい！
Yes!

856
01:02:54,738 --> 01:02:57,438
配信後にこちらMVが、えーと、公開されます
After the stream, the MV will be released!

857
01:02:57,438 --> 01:03:00,738
多分、こっそり今マネちゃんがプレミア公開に切り替えてくれているはず
My manager is probably stealthily switching it to a premiere release right now!

858
01:03:00,738 --> 01:03:04,938
楽曲は0時リリースになっております！
The song will be released digitally at midnight!

859
01:03:04,938 --> 01:03:06,438
はい！
Yes!

860
01:03:06,438 --> 01:03:08,638
そしてあの、ちょっと気付いた人もいるかもしれないんですけど
And some of you might have already noticed,

861
01:03:08,638 --> 01:03:13,338
ジャケットの文字は風真いろはさんが自分で書きました、はい。ありがとうございます
but the text on the jacket art was hand-written by me! Yes, thank you very much.

862
01:03:13,338 --> 01:03:15,438
ということで
So with that said,

863
01:03:15,438 --> 01:03:17,438
もう終わっちゃうんですけど
we're already nearing the end,

864
01:03:17,438 --> 01:03:20,638
なんか、すごいトレンド2位とかに入ってるっていう連絡を受けました！うそ！
but I just received word that we're trending at number 2! No way!

865
01:03:20,638 --> 01:03:23,338
あと残り頑張ってくれと言いたいけど
I want to tell you to keep pushing for the top, but...

866
01:03:23,338 --> 01:03:27,838
でもみんな本当にいっぱいポストしてくれてありがとうね！
anyway, thank you all so much for posting so much!

867
01:03:27,838 --> 01:03:28,938
よし、準備できた？
Alright, are you ready?

868
01:03:28,938 --> 01:03:31,138
音の準備は全部できてそうなので
It looks like all the audio setup is complete,

869
01:03:31,138 --> 01:03:34,938
早速、新曲歌っていきたいと思います！
so I'm going to perform my new song right away!

870
01:03:34,938 --> 01:03:36,238
しかし、しかし！
However, however!

871
01:03:36,238 --> 01:03:38,338
今回はちょっと特別なものを用意してきました！
I've prepared something a bit special for this!

872
01:03:38,338 --> 01:03:41,338
ゴンドラ、来い！
Gondola, come on out!

873
01:03:41,338 --> 01:03:45,438
おお！
Oh!

874
01:03:45,438 --> 01:03:49,138
リハーサルで見たけど、やっぱいいなこれ！
I saw it during rehearsal, but this is really great!

875
01:03:49,138 --> 01:03:52,338
ほっ、というわけで
Up we go! So with that,

876
01:03:52,338 --> 01:03:55,338
みんな、ぽこべえがいなくて寂しかったでしょ？
you guys were lonely without Pokobe, right?

877
01:03:55,338 --> 01:03:58,438
今年は、ゴンドラになりました！
This year, he became a gondola!

878
01:03:58,438 --> 01:04:02,238
はい、というわけで、早速やっていくんですが
Yes, so we'll get started right away, but...

879
01:04:02,238 --> 01:04:04,738
ドア、オープン！
Door, open!

880
01:04:04,738 --> 01:04:09,638
イェーイ、ほっ！乗っちゃおうね！
Yay, up! Let's get on!

881
01:04:09,638 --> 01:04:11,338
というわけで！
So with that...

882
01:04:11,338 --> 01:04:13,338
早速、歌っていきたいと思います
I'd like to perform the song right away.

883
01:04:13,338 --> 01:04:15,938
それでは聴いてください。風真いろは、新オリジナル曲
Please listen to my new original song,

884
01:04:15,938 --> 01:04:19,638
「風向きエントロピー」
"Kazamuki Entropy."

885
01:04:21,138 --> 01:04:29,138
風向きエントロピー
作詞・作曲・編曲：40mP
Kazamuki Entropy
Lyrics, Composition, Arrangement: 40mP

886
01:04:37,538 --> 01:04:41,138
ねえ いつからそこにあったの？
Hey, when did you get there?

887
01:04:41,138 --> 01:04:45,438
あまりにも近すぎて気づかなかったよ
It was so close, I didn't even notice.

888
01:04:45,438 --> 01:04:49,138
ずっと私が生まれた日から
You've been by my side

889
01:04:49,138 --> 01:04:52,638
そばにいてくれたのにね
since the day I was born, haven't you?

890
01:04:52,638 --> 01:04:54,138
曖昧で
Ambiguous...

891
01:04:54,138 --> 01:04:56,138
複雑で
...complex...

892
01:04:56,138 --> 01:04:57,738
予測不可能で
...and unpredictable,

893
01:04:57,738 --> 01:05:00,138
気まぐれに変わってゆく空の模様
the ever-changing appearance of the sky.

894
01:05:00,186 --> 01:05:01,486
想像していたより
More than I had imagined...

895
01:05:01,486 --> 01:05:04,086
うまく笑えない
I can't smile properly...

896
01:05:04,386 --> 01:05:07,386
だけどそれ以上に
But even more than that,

897
01:05:07,386 --> 01:05:11,586
世界は優しくて
the world is so gentle.

898
01:05:11,886 --> 01:05:15,686
いつか風が生まれた
One day, a wind was born

899
01:05:15,686 --> 01:05:18,686
足跡が始まる場所
at the place where footprints begin.

900
01:05:18,886 --> 01:05:22,386
あの日の未来が帰って
Even if the future from that day returns

901
01:05:22,386 --> 01:05:24,486
駆けだしたとしても
and starts running...

902
01:05:24,486 --> 01:05:26,786
ここに来るんだろう
I would still end up right here, wouldn't I?

903
01:05:27,686 --> 01:05:29,186
この景色も
This scenery...

904
01:05:29,186 --> 01:05:31,186
この声も
and this voice...

905
01:05:31,386 --> 01:05:34,386
私を彩るすべて
everything that colors my life.

906
01:05:34,386 --> 01:05:36,186
方向なんて
As for the direction,

907
01:05:36,186 --> 01:05:37,486
まだ
I still...

908
01:05:37,486 --> 01:05:40,686
わからないけど
don't know it yet, but...

909
01:05:40,686 --> 01:05:44,386
ただ風の吹くままに
I will just go where the wind blows.

910
01:06:00,186 --> 01:06:03,386
ねえ いつから気づいてたの？
Tell me, since when did you know?

911
01:06:03,386 --> 01:06:07,186
まるで私のこと全部お見通しで
It's like you can see right through everything about me.

912
01:06:07,386 --> 01:06:11,186
苦し紛れにごまかした嘘も
Even the lies I used to scrape by...

913
01:06:11,186 --> 01:06:14,486
君にはバレてたのかな
I wonder if you had them all figured out.

914
01:06:14,686 --> 01:06:17,486
平凡で退屈で
An ordinary, boring,

915
01:06:17,486 --> 01:06:19,186
あくび混じりで
yawn-filled,

916
01:06:19,186 --> 01:06:22,486
変化のないありふれてる時間
and unchanging routine time...

917
01:06:22,486 --> 01:06:24,686
想像していただけじゃ
If I just kept imagining things,

918
01:06:24,686 --> 01:06:26,986
何も変わらない
nothing would change.

919
01:06:27,186 --> 01:06:30,186
だけどそれ以上に
But even more than that,

920
01:06:30,186 --> 01:06:33,186
予測していた以上に
even more than I predicted,

921
01:06:33,186 --> 01:06:34,186
ほら
look,

922
01:06:34,186 --> 01:06:37,986
新しい風が吹いてきて
a new wind has started to blow.

923
01:06:38,186 --> 01:06:40,186
不器用な自分が
And my clumsy self...

924
01:06:40,186 --> 01:06:45,186
愛おしく思えたんだ
started to feel quite precious to me.

925
01:07:01,186 --> 01:07:04,986
いつか風が止んで
Someday, when the wind stops...

926
01:07:04,986 --> 01:07:08,686
足跡が途切れた場所
at the place where footprints fade away...

927
01:07:08,686 --> 01:07:11,686
落とし物探して 拾って
I'll search for lost things and pick them up.

928
01:07:11,686 --> 01:07:13,986
見つけだせたから
Since I managed to find them,

929
01:07:13,986 --> 01:07:17,686
ここにいるんだろう
I must be standing right here.

930
01:07:17,686 --> 01:07:18,686
そっと
Softly,

931
01:07:18,686 --> 01:07:20,686
髪がなびく
my hair flutters in the wind.

932
01:07:20,686 --> 01:07:24,686
いつか風が夢見た
Someday, the wind dreamed...

933
01:07:24,686 --> 01:07:27,686
青空と交わる場所
of the place where it meets the blue sky.

934
01:07:27,686 --> 01:07:31,186
回り道選んで 迷って
Choosing detours and getting lost...

935
01:07:31,186 --> 01:07:33,186
躓いたとしても
even if I stumble along the way,

936
01:07:33,186 --> 01:07:35,986
そこへ行くんだろう
I will still make my way there.

937
01:07:36,186 --> 01:07:37,686
この景色も
This scenery...

938
01:07:37,686 --> 01:07:39,686
この声も
and this voice...

939
01:07:39,686 --> 01:07:42,686
私を彩るすべて
everything that colors my life...

940
01:07:42,686 --> 01:07:45,486
等身大の手で
With my own hands,

941
01:07:45,486 --> 01:07:50,186
握りしめて
I will hold onto them tightly.

942
01:07:50,686 --> 01:07:53,486
想像以上にもっと
More than I ever imagined,

943
01:07:53,486 --> 01:07:57,686
自由な速度で
at a freer pace.

944
01:07:58,386 --> 01:08:00,186
方向なんて
As for the direction,

945
01:08:00,186 --> 01:08:01,286
まだ
I still...

946
01:08:01,286 --> 01:08:04,686
わからないけど
don't know it yet, but...

947
01:08:04,686 --> 01:08:08,686
ただ風の吹くままに
I will just go where the wind blows.

948
01:08:25,386 --> 01:08:29,186
はい！というわけで、ありがとうございました！
And with that, thank you so much!

949
01:08:29,386 --> 01:08:32,986
よいしょ。みんな、すっかり忘れてると思うけど
Alright! I think everyone has completely forgotten, but...

950
01:08:33,186 --> 01:08:37,186
今日これ、これから、記念撮影します！
today, we are going to take a commemorative photo!

951
01:08:37,386 --> 01:08:40,386
そう、お土産があるって言ったっしょ？
That's right! I said there would be a souvenir, right?

952
01:08:40,486 --> 01:08:43,886
これこれ、いや、ちょっと待って、マジで自撮り棒
This, this... No, wait a minute. Seriously, this selfie stick...

953
01:08:43,986 --> 01:08:46,686
これリハーサルでめっちゃ練習したのに！
Even though I practiced with it so much in rehearsal!

954
01:08:46,786 --> 01:08:49,386
自撮り棒下手。あ、いい感じいい感じ。
I'm bad with selfie sticks. Oh, this is good, this is good.

955
01:08:49,686 --> 01:08:51,686
カシャ。
Click!

956
01:08:53,186 --> 01:08:55,986
よし。いけてそう、いけてそう。
Alright, looks like it worked, looks like it worked.

957
01:08:56,186 --> 01:08:57,386
オッケー！
Okay!

958
01:08:57,486 --> 01:08:59,986
はい！というわけで皆さん
So, everyone!

959
01:09:00,186 --> 01:09:04,186
今日お土産ありって言いましたね？
I did say there would be a souvenir today, right?

960
01:09:04,286 --> 01:09:10,686
そうなんです。今日撮った、今この風真がね、自撮り棒で撮った写真が
That's right. The picture that I, Kazama, just took with the selfie stick...

961
01:09:10,686 --> 01:09:13,986
コンビニで、なんとプリントアウトできます！
can actually be printed out at convenience stores!

962
01:09:14,386 --> 01:09:16,686
すごい！
That's amazing!

963
01:09:17,186 --> 01:09:22,186
はい、こちらですね、対象店舗、ファミリーマートさん、ローソンさん、ミニストップさんで
Yes, this one. Available at FamilyMart, Lawson, and Ministop...

964
01:09:22,186 --> 01:09:26,186
本日21時から、ネットで事前購入ができます。
you can pre-purchase online starting from 9 PM today.

965
01:09:26,286 --> 01:09:29,686
お値段がですね、税込300円とのことで、
The price is 300 yen including tax, and...

966
01:09:29,786 --> 01:09:35,486
印刷できるのは、明日6月19日の20時からになっております。
you will be able to print it starting tomorrow, June 19th, from 8 PM.

967
01:09:35,586 --> 01:09:39,986
写真にはですね、複製手書きメッセージ、この後書きますんで。
On the photo, there will be a printed handwritten message, which I'll write after this.

968
01:09:40,086 --> 01:09:44,886
はい、どんな写真が撮れているか、写真下手くそでも怒らないでね？
So please look forward to it. And don't get mad if the photo turned out bad, okay?

969
01:09:44,986 --> 01:09:48,486
内容は買ってから確認してください。
Please check the content after you buy it.

970
01:09:48,986 --> 01:09:50,486
いや、すごいよね？
I mean, isn't that amazing?

971
01:09:50,586 --> 01:09:56,186
ちょっと一足早く皆さんのもとに、手元に残るライブのお土産が用意できればということで
I really wanted to prepare a physical live concert souvenir that you can hold onto,

972
01:09:56,286 --> 01:10:00,186
今回やらせていただきました。お土産あります！
so we put this together. Enjoy your souvenir!

973
01:10:00,161 --> 01:10:04,361
ちょっと皆さん 各自で回収って形で それだけが申し訳ないんですが
I'm sorry that you have to go and collect it yourselves,

974
01:10:04,361 --> 01:10:08,661
お土産ありますので ぜひ気になったらコンビニでプリントしてみてください！
but it's a souvenir! If you're interested, please try printing it at a convenience store!

975
01:10:09,061 --> 01:10:14,561
そして コンビニプリント購入できるのは 7月21日17時59分までです！
Also, the convenience store print will be available for purchase until July 21st at 17:59!

976
01:10:14,661 --> 01:10:21,961
概要欄に 写真購入のリンク、多分今マネちゃんがやってくれてると思いますので よろしくお願いします！
The link to purchase the photo is in the description! My manager is probably putting it up now, so please check it out!

977
01:10:22,661 --> 01:10:27,661
そしてこの後はですね MVの公開と メンバーシップ限定のアンコールライブありますので
And after this, we have the MV release and the membership-exclusive encore live...

978
01:10:27,661 --> 01:10:31,061
そちらも絶対に聴いてくださいね！
...so please make sure to tune in to those as well!

979
01:10:31,661 --> 01:10:35,461
それでは皆さん またお会いしましょう！
Well then, everyone, see you again!

980
01:10:35,461 --> 01:10:41,161
最高の誕生日でした！バイバーイ！
This was the best birthday ever! Bye-bye!

